<Heading Level="HeadingLevel.H2">Dropdown Component</Heading>
<Paragraph>
    Dropdowns are menus that display a list of links and other elements. Dropdowns can be toggled.
</Paragraph>


<DocsSection ComponentName="Dropdown" />


<Heading Id="examples" IsAnchor="true" Level="HeadingLevel.H3" MarginTop="Spacing.Five">Examples</Heading>
<Paragraph>
    The two examples below shows the variations you can have with the <code>Dropdown</code> component.
</Paragraph>

<Dropdown>
    <DropdownToggleLink Text="Text toggle" />
    <DropdownMenu>
        <DropdownItem Text="Active" IsActive="true" />
        <DropdownItem Text="Disabled" IsDisabled="true" />
        <DropdownDivider />
        <DropdownItem Text="Normal" />
    </DropdownMenu>
</Dropdown>


